item.title: I press run.bat but my server isnt going online? someone please help?
item.dc:creator: @doom_j doom_j
item.description:
@doom_j wrote:

use canyouseeme.org if it cannot see that the port is open then you either didn’t port forward correctly with your router or you didn’t add an exception to your firewall.

A good test for the firewall is to shut it off and then use canyouseeme.org if you connect then it was you’re firewall, if you still cannot connect then you need to make sure you port forwarded correctly on your router.
